pesticide.PPE: Applicators and other handlers must wear long-sleeved shirt and long pants, socks and shoes.

Active_Ingredients.name: Glyphosate, N-(phosphonomethyl)glycine, in the form of its isopropylamine salt
Active_Ingredients.mode_Of_Action: Inhibits an enzyme essential to the formation of specific amino acids

Safety_Information.general_Info: Keep Out of Reach of Children. CAUTION. FOR MEDICAL ASSISTANCE, CALL COLLECT, DAY OR NIGHT, 1-(800) 334-7577.
